==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[tres chic]] (English naturalized spelling)
*[[tre chic]] (common misspelling)

===Etymology===
From [[French]].  Literally "very stylish."

===Phrase===
'''[[très]] [[chic]]'''

# {{colloquial}} An [[expression]] that something is in [[style]] and/or [[desirable]].

===Quotations===
